code: @Override public void acknowledgeCheckpoint(JobID jobID, ExecutionAttemptID executionAttemptID, long checkpointId, CheckpointMetrics checkpointMetrics, TaskStateSnapshot subtaskState) {     checkpointCoordinatorGateway.acknowledgeCheckpoint(jobID, executionAttemptID, checkpointId, checkpointMetrics, subtaskState). }

@Override public void declineCheckpoint(JobID jobID, ExecutionAttemptID executionAttemptID, long checkpointId, Throwable cause) {     checkpointCoordinatorGateway.declineCheckpoint(new DeclineCheckpoint(jobID, executionAttemptID, checkpointId, cause)). }
